name: Michaelynn Welther
tagline: Freelance Tutor. Student. Beginning Web Developer.
body:
### About Me
As a California native with a determined mindset, embracing the idea of "work hard, play hard" comes naturally to me. I am a recent graduate of El Segundo High School, and will be attending Cal Poly, San Luis Obispo, in the fall to study Applied Mathematics. I participated in my school's band and robotics teams, maintained above a 4.0 GPA, and taught myself Italian, HTML, and CSS on the side. On my free time I enjoy listening to music, hanging out with friends, learning new skills, browsing the Internet, and going to new places to try new things.
